    "The models showed proficiency in information extraction and responding to structured questions, with accuracy rates between 88 and 98%.",
    "However, their effectiveness diminished down to 50-70% in making clinical decisions, underscoring a gap in their application.",
    "In breast cancer care, attention to detail is crucial.",
